# Frontend Environment Variables

# API Configuration
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5001/api

# Application Configuration
VITE_APP_NAME=Team Tracker

# 📧 EMAIL SYSTEM INFORMATION
# Email functionality is handled by the backend
# To configure email providers, edit backend/.env file
#
# 📝 EMAIL SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. To use Gmail: Set GMAIL_USER and GMAIL_PASS in backend/.env
# 2. To use Outlook: Set OUTLOOK_USER and OUTLOOK_PASS in backend/.env
# 3. To use Yahoo: Set YAHOO_USER and YAHOO_PASS in backend/.env
# 4. If no provider is configured, test emails will be used
# 5. Test emails can be viewed at: https://ethereal.email
#
# Current Status: Test mode (view emails at https://ethereal.email)
